page.title: 10LAURA WEBB'S DAY
page.content: I wake at 7.30a.m. and get up after 5 minutes. I go into the bathroom and wash and dress.I go downstairs and pick up the letters and make my breakfast.I eat while I watch T.V.I prepare my lunch,brush my teeth and leave for school.We have Assembly first and then we usually have Maths.We have a break with milk and biscuits at 10.35 and finish the morning with English work. We have our lunch at 12 and I usually have a Breakaway bar, two pieces of brown bread and butter and a carton of yoghurt.Work starts again at 1.15p.m. and we have lessons such as Art until 2.30 when we have a break of 10 minutes.After this we finish off various pieces of work until we finish at 3.45.I go home and play games on my Spectrum computer.I heat a Beefburger in our microwave oven and go to bed at 9.45.
